          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "In the landscape of AI APIs, ben2q provides a scalable inference engine tailored for high-throughput applications. This guide offers actionable insights for API teams to integrate Ben2 with ben2q into production environments, emphasizing practical configuration and optimization."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "h2",
