          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Setting Up Your Ben2 Environment"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Begin by provisioning your infrastructure. Ensure you have a compatible runtime, such as Docker or a Kubernetes cluster, with sufficient GPU resources for ben2q. Install the Ben2 client library via pip: "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "pip install ben2-client",
            "code": true
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ". Configure environment variables for API keys and endpoints, and validate connectivity with a health check endpoint."
          }
        ]
      },
