        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Optimize inference latency and throughput by tuning ben2q parameters. Use batch processing for concurrent requests and adjust model quantization settings based on your hardware. Below is a compact table of key ben2q configuration options:"
